","title":"Delivery Information","description":"&lt;p&gt;Delivery Information&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Delivery Information","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"38","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Fire Slider","description":"&lt;h1&gt;Advanced content and image slider with video support and animated captions.&lt;\/h1&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Create elegant fixed dimensions or full width sliders in no time! Fire slider is suitable for both simple slides (e.g. image only slideshow) and complex slides with inside animation.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Advanced layer options allow the user to create complex caption animation and turn a static image in an eye catching interactive banner. You can control animation type, speed, delay and easing; add start and end opacity, rotation and scale; set font size, text align and color.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Fire slider is fully responsive and will perfectly adapt to any screen resolution. Full width sliders have the option to become responsive for a specified screen size. Navigation is mobile optimized with touch swipe enabled.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Although fire slider has some very advanced options, you are not bound to use them. Plain image slides can be created quick and easy.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Fire Slider","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"14","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Font options","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Advanced Typography and Font Options!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The extended font settings, that come with&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 17.1428px;&quot;&gt;Burn Engine&lt;\/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;allow you to control every single piece of text in your web store. You can change font family, style and size, or set letter and word spacing. All elements will have their line height automatically set based on font size and a&amp;nbsp;global line height, which you can change.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Burn Engine gives you the option to use both system and 630+ free Google fonts to bring a unique look to your website. All custom fonts can be subset (latin, cyrillic etc.) and use only the characters that you actually need and thus reducing loading times.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Individual font options are available for each content block and Page Builder row for more styling flexibility.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Font options","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"36","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Free Support &amp; Updates","description":"&lt;h2&gt;We Offer Free Support &amp;amp; Updates for All Our Themes!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A premium theme must not only be made with appealing look at the front and smart coding at the back. It also needs strong and continuous commitment by the developers' team to ensure its longevity.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kiddos theme comes with a premium support. Our dedicated team of professionals will do whatever it takes to fix any possible issues that may come up or help our customers, if they need any 'how to' guidance. Your problems are our problems!&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theme future development comes as a second important task for our team. Compatibility upgrades will be provided as quickly as possible, as well as free new features requested by our users.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Free Support &amp; Updates","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"30","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Google maps","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Google maps","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"21","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Grids","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Grids","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"55","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Home (fullscreen slider)","description":"&lt;p&gt;Home (Fullscreen slider)&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Home (fullscreen slider)","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"56","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Home (transparent header)","description":"&lt;p&gt;Home (transparent header)&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Home (transparent header)","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"17","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Home ver.2","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Home ver.2","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"18","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Home ver.3","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Home ver.3","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"19","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Home ver.4","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Home ver.4","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"20","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Home ver.5","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Home ver.5","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"24","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Icon Lists","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Icon Lists","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"23","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Image &amp; Video","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Image &amp; Video","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"42","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Live preview","description":"&lt;h2&gt;No more save and refresh! See your changes live!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Most of the time a site is configured through its backend so you need to refresh the frontend in order to preview the changes. This could turn into tedious sequence of \u2018save\u2019 and \u2018refresh\u2019 clicks if you want to fine tune the site\u2019s appearance.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;It is time to take advantage of the Burn Engine \u2018Live Preview\u2019 feature, which allows your page to be viewable from the admin panel. You can make changes to colors and fonts, modify the main navigation, style product listings and product information pages, use Page Builder and see all the changes right away.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Live preview","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"32","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Menu Composer","description":"&lt;h2&gt;An advanced menu management for OpenCart!&lt;\/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Menu Composer allows you to quickly build your custom store navigation. You can combine categories, information and system pages, external links, custom HTML dropdown, all categories and brands listings. The intuitive drag &amp;amp; drop interface help you to easily rearrange menu items and with only a few clicks. Megamenus can be set for categories, category and brands listings.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your navigation will automatically adapt for smaller screen and will behave nicely on touch devices.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Menu Composer","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"45","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"More Features","description":"&lt;p&gt;Burn Engine has so many features we just couldn\u2019t list them all in the demo site. It is actually impossible to demonstrate them all because many of the features combine with other to produce unique visual and functional combinations. Some of the not mentioned options are:&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;tb_list_1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Text logo&lt;\/strong&gt; - use a plain text logo with custom font instead of an image.&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Store control&lt;\/strong&gt; - you can enable\/disable some e-commerce related functions - brands, compare, wishlist, checkout, gift voucher, affiliate, returns&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subcategories style &lt;\/strong&gt;- includes a single line subcategories in a slider, several display styles and an option to list next level categories&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Custom buttons&lt;\/strong&gt; - set a custom \u201cadd to cart\u201d button text according to the stock status of the respective product&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Site width&lt;\/strong&gt; - change the maximum side width&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System messages&lt;\/strong&gt; - manage appearance of system messages&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background&lt;\/strong&gt; - set store background globally or for specific information page\/category&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Payment images&lt;\/strong&gt; - add payment images at the bottom next to copyright information.&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Custom code&lt;\/strong&gt; - apply custom stylesheets and javascript through admin panel without having to edit files&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;tb_mb_10&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Social integration&lt;\/strong&gt; - setup social widgets (Facebook, Twitter) with different locales&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n&lt;\/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;It\u2019s up to you to discover the countless Pavilion possibilities and use them according to your needs. Of course, more features will come with the theme updates as we will watch closely your requests.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Stay tuned!&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"More Features","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"10","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Multi-store Ready","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Real Multi-store support!&lt;\/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;http:\/\/www.opencart.com\/index.php?route=feature\/feature&amp;amp;path=4&quot;&gt;OpenCart multi-store&lt;\/a&gt; functionality is a useful feature that allows you to use one database for different stores (domains) for easier management. Usually same theme settings apply to each store that use identical theme.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 17.1428px;&quot;&gt;Burn Engine&lt;\/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;however makes possible to use&amp;nbsp;separate theme settings for every single store.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can have different general settings, colors and fonts, style individually each website area (header, menu, intro, content wrap, footer), create custom layouts, page content and sidebars. All this lets you manage unique stores under a single administration panel.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Multi-store Ready","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"16","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Page Builder","description":"&lt;h2&gt;The missing OpenCart advanced CMS is finally here!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Page Builder replaces the default OpenCart module\/layout functionality with an advanced system which allows you to control the entire page content and style. Technically, the layout is based on a &lt;a href=&quot;grids&quot;&gt;extended responsive CSS grid system&lt;\/a&gt;, similar to Bootstrap, Pure or Foundation. The concept is close to Visual Composer for WordPress.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Page Builder is the ultimate landing page creator. Use it to design your lead capture pages, improving SEO and conversion rate from online advertisements. Quickly build different versions when testing for landing page optimization. No need to use external lander generators.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the aid of an convenient drag &amp;amp; drop interface you don't need much time to build complex layouts. No programming skills are required - just your imagination!&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Burn Engine comes with 25 built-in content blocks (just like WordPress widgets) packed with functionality and styling options, which permit countless page variations.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You are now the designer!&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Page Builder","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"31","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Performance Optimization","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Performance is of an importance!&lt;\/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Regardless of how astonishing your site looks, none of the users will be able to enjoy it if it performs slowly and takes ages for pages to load. The website speed is a crucial factor when fighting for potential customers. We take this challenge very seriously and have made significant performance testing while developing our theme. As a result E uses different techniques&amp;nbsp; to improve the server and client side rendering speed.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All of the content builder blocks are cached on the server to reduce the time needed to send them to the user. You can control the cache settings for every individual block to make sure the information it provides is fresh enough. &amp;nbsp;&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The system classes of the theme are automatically merged into one file to skip fetching them one by one on every request. We have analyzed OpenCart queries very closely and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 17.1428px;&quot;&gt;Burn Engine&lt;\/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;adds some important indexes upon install, which optimize some database queries.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We followed closely the Google best practices for client-side performance. The frontend styles and scripts are combined, minified and statically served to the browser, which reduces load time and takes advantage of browser caching.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We also provide easy CDN integration - if you host your resources on a cloud delivery network you just need to change a single option in the theme\u2019s settings.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Additionally we provide an optional vQmod extension which makes further improvements for sites with larger databases. This helps&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 17.1428px;&quot;&gt;Kiddos&lt;\/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;to perform great on installations with thousands of products and categories and there is no need to install additional caching&amp;nbsp;modules.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The various performance enhancements make Kiddos suitable for shared hosting.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Performance Optimization","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"3","bottom":"1","sort_order":"3","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Privacy Policy","description":"&lt;p&gt;This privacy policy has been compiled to better serve those who are concerned with how their 'Personally identifiable information' is being used online.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Please read our privacy policy carefully to get a clear understanding of how we collect, use, protect or otherwise handle your Personally Identifiable Information in accordance with our website.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;What information do we collect?&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;When registering on our site, as appropriate, you may be asked to enter your Name, Email address or other details to help you with your experience.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;How do we use your information?&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We may use the information we collect from you when you register, sign up for our newsletter, respond to a survey or marketing communication, surf the website, or use certain other site features to allow us to better service you in responding to your customer service requests.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Third Party Disclosure&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer Personally Identifiable Information. We do not include or offer third party products or services on our website.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Privacy Policy","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"35","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Product Listing Styles","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Customize your product listing up to the smallest detail!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You can choose between 3 different list styles: plain - no visual separation between different products; bordered - products are separate by a subtle border; separate each product is an individual box with background color. You have also the option to set different add to cart\/wishlist\/compare design and position; add product box and product thumbnail hover states; change products per row and spacing between products.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The unique &quot;elements visibility&quot; feature, give you the power to control, which product element to show or hide for a specific product listing for a given state. E.g you can leave only product thumbnails visible by default and show all other information on mouse hover.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The combinations are unlimited!&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Product Listing Styles","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"27","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Responsive Banners","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Responsive Banners","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"8","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Responsive Design","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Fully functional on any device and resolution!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the ever-increasing mobile usage the importance of responsive design today is beyond any doubt. It gives you SEO advantages, increases conversion rates and has positive effect to the website earnings.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kiddos is not only cross-browser compatible. It is built to support devices with different resolutions. The theme can adapt to every screen size thanks to its responsiveness - all assets scale down to fit the smaller screen space. Products per row adjust automatically based on what you've set in the theme options panel. Also the theme\u2019s navigation controls support touch swipe functionality where appropriate (sliders or carousels e.g.). Hover dropdown menus are supported as well.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;All this means that your store will look and behave nicely on mobile devices (smartphones and tablets), laptop or desktop computer.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The responsive features of the theme are implemented strictly according to latest Google guidelines and recommendations.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Responsive Design","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"37","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"RTL Language Support","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Right-to-left language support out of the box&lt;\/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;While developing Burn Engine, we wanted the theme to be a truly multi-language system. As a result, Burn Engine has a full right-to-left language (Arabic, Hebrew etc.) support. Language direction is auto detected and works out of the box.&lt;\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In RTL mode \u0430ll elements change their direction from right to left: site logo (unless put in the center), the grid system columns, products in product listing, icon position, form labels and fields. All of this without having to do manual adjustments and configurations.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"RTL Language Support","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"11","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Sample data","description":"&lt;h2&gt;One click demo data installation!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kiddos comes packaged with dummy content data you can enable after theme installation. The sample data option will bring all the content&lt;sup&gt;*&lt;\/sup&gt; from the demo website into your store. This will help you to setup your theme and start selling faster!&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Products, categories, information pages, menus, sidebars and theme settings will be created for you with a single click. You can choose which of the demo designs to import. For customers with existing stores and content, there is the option to import only the theme design.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;tb_text_str_3&quot;&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;sup&gt;*&lt;\/sup&gt;Demo product images will be replaced with those that come with the default OpenCart installation.&lt;\/small&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Sample data","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"22","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Shop","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Shop","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"26","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Social","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Social","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"43","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Sticky Header","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Always accessible navigation&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;It is known that one of the most important components of a website is the navigation. An easy to use or access navigation can lead to better user experience and decrease the bounce rate.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;In most of the websites as soon we start scrolling down the page the header navigation is left out of the visible window area. The user must scroll back to the top of the website in order to access it. The Kiddos sticky header solves this annoying issue - it sticks at the top of the page and stands always at your disposal.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;According to a Smashing Magazine study sticky menus are 22% easier to navigate than the traditional ones.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Sticky Header","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"39","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Style Editor","description":"&lt;h2&gt;Unlimited Styling Combinations!&lt;\/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Style Editor allows you to control the style of nearly every theme component - Page Builder rows, blocks, header, content, footer or the entire store wrapper.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You can control the margin, padding and column spacing for each area, define column size, set border and border radius, apply multiple shadows and attach multiple backgrounds. Backgrounds can be either images, or linear and radial gradients.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Everything comes with an intuitive interface - fast and easy to use.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;No coding skills are required and you can check the applied effects real time with the aid of a &lt;a href=&quot;style-editor&quot;&gt;Photoshop like style preview&lt;\/a&gt;.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Style Editor","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"28","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Tabs","description":"&lt;p&gt;asd&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"Tabs","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"5","bottom":"1","sort_order":"4","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Terms &amp; Conditions","description":"&lt;p&gt;Welcome to pavilion-theme.com. If you continue to browse and use this website, you are agreeing to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions of use, which together with our &lt;a href=&quot;\/privacy-policy&quot;&gt;privacy policy&lt;\/a&gt; govern themeburn's relationship with you in relation to this website.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&