inistration area for easier use. Of course, you can break the inheritance tree and fine-tune every single color to match your specific needs.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;\u201cUnlimited possibilities\u201d is not a metaphor when speaking for colors configuration in Kiddos.&lt;\/p&gt;","meta_title":"Unlimited Colors","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"40","bottom":"0","sort_order":"0","status":"1","language_id":"2","title":"Unlimited Header Variations","description":"&lt;p&gt;Every webmaster has own preferences for the header structure and wants to arrange its elements differently. The main idea behind Burn Engine is to give you maximum flexibility while configuring your webstore, so you can choose between 8 header variants (more to come).&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Some of the header configurations has the main navigation positioned as a separate area that can be additionally styled.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Observe how the elements (site logo, links, currency and language switchers, cart and search box) are arranged in every header variant and select the layout that best fits your needs.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n","meta_title":"8 Header Variations","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""}]